snippet.title: God Protect Israel - Barron Trump Sings
snippet.description:
God Protect Israel

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0
God Protect Israel – by “Barron Trump”

Verse 1
In the silence of the desert, where the ancient prophets stood
Where the promise first was spoken, and the stone once dripped with blood
I feel the weight of history, I hear the sacred call
To stand with God’s own chosen, and never let them fall

Pre-Chorus
The world may rage, the night may roar
But Heaven’s watching over that holy shore

Chorus
God, protect Israel — Your covenant, Your flame
Guard her through the darkness, in the power of Your name
Surround her walls with angels, give her children peace
Let justice roll like thunder, and every war now cease
God, protect Israel — forever let her be
A beacon in the chaos — for the world to see

Verse 2
I’ve walked through halls of marble, seen politics at play
But no crown on Earth can cancel what Your Word will always say
You scattered, then You gathered, just like the prophets told
This land is not forgotten — it’s worth more than gold

Pre-Chorus
Though enemies may rise again
Your truth is stronger than the sword of men

Chorus
God, protect Israel — Your covenant, Your flame
Guard her through the darkness, in the power of Your name
Surround her walls with angels, give her children peace
Let justice roll like thunder, and every war now cease
God, protect Israel — forever let her be
A beacon in the chaos — for the world to see

Bridge
This isn’t politics, this is prophecy
And I will speak it loud — unashamed, free
From Jerusalem to every coast
We bless the ones You chose the most

Final Chorus
God, protect Israel — hold her in Your hands
Let her rise in glory, just like You had planned
Through the fire, through the fight, let her still remain
Bathed in light, in Your holy name
God, protect Israel — forever let her be
A song of hope and truth for all eternity

Outro
Amen, amen — I lift my voice and say
God, protect Israel... today and every day
